    "body": "On CORAL, LLVM will use the XL Fortran compiler and I need to apply a change for the xl_r compiler to the clang compiler to make netlib-lapack build w/clang+xlf.\r\n\r\nI split the xl_r patch in two: one specific to xl_r, that removes the -qfixed flag from Fortran compile options; and one that fixes the CBLAS use of default mangling definitions.",
